
### 7. Create the zip file:

To create the final zip file, run these commands:

```bash
# Create the complete project
cd portfolio-as-a-service

# Install dependencies (optional, removes node_modules from zip)
npm install --prefix backend
npm install --prefix frontend

# Create zip
zip -r portfolio-as-a-service.zip . -x "*/node_modules/*" "*/.git/*" "*.log"

# Or use tar for better compression
tar -czf portfolio-as-a-service.tar.gz --exclude="node_modules" --exclude=".git" .